channel.title: Endgame :: SANS Holiday Hack Challenge 2025
channel.description: Upon completing the game I met the entire Counter Hack team over at the Grand Hotel: Clicking Santa and he spilled the tea: Magnificent work, my friends! You’ve saved the Dosis Neighborhood from an eternal winter and stopped those mischievous Gnomes from causing any more trouble. But Frosty… oh, Frosty. I understand your fear of melting, truly I do. The pain of fading away each spring, knowing you’ll disappear until the next winter snow falls - that must be terribly lonely.
